# Slack macOS Keybindings
# Format: category|keybinding|description
# Users can override these in ~/.config/keybinds/slack.conf

# Navigation
Navigation|Cmd+K|Quick Switcher - jump to any conversation
Navigation|Cmd+T|Jump to conversation - search by name
Navigation|Cmd+G|Go to previous conversation
Navigation|Cmd+[|Older conversation
Navigation|Cmd+]|Newer conversation
Navigation|Page Up|Scroll up in channel
Navigation|Page Down|Scroll down in channel
Navigation|Cmd+↑|Jump to first unread message
Navigation|Cmd+↓|Jump to first unread message
Navigation|Alt+Up|Jump to previous conversation
Navigation|Alt+Down|Jump to next conversation

# Messaging & Composing
Messaging|Cmd+Enter|Send message
Messaging|Shift+Enter|New line in message
Messaging|Cmd+/|Search current channel
Messaging|Cmd+?|View shortcuts and commands
Messaging|Cmd+U|Upload file
Messaging|Ctrl+Enter|Create thread reply
Messaging|Cmd+B|Bold text
Messaging|Cmd+I|Italic text
Messaging|Cmd+Shift+X|Strikethrough text
Messaging|Cmd+`|Code block
Messaging|Cmd+Shift+]|Indent code block

# Reactions & Threads
Reactions|Cmd+R|Show reaction picker (in thread)
Reactions|Cmd+Y|Show emoji panel
Threads|Cmd+T|Open message details
Threads|Cmd+Shift+T|Go to parent message

# Search
Search|Cmd+F|Search current channel
Search|Cmd+Shift+F|Search all conversations
Search|Cmd+L|Clear search

# Workspace & Preferences
Workspace|Cmd+,|Open Preferences
Workspace|Cmd+Shift+H|Show Home
Workspace|Cmd+;|Show saved items
Workspace|Cmd+'|Show draft messages
Workspace|Cmd+J|Open file browser
Workspace|Ctrl+Tab|Switch to next workspace
Workspace|Ctrl+Shift+Tab|Switch to previous workspace

# Calls & Media
Calls|Cmd+Shift+U|Mute/unmute (in call)
Calls|Cmd+Shift+V|Start/stop video (in call)
Calls|Cmd+Shift+S|Share screen (in call)
Calls|Esc|Leave call

# Status & Presence
Status|Cmd+.|Set status
Status|Cmd+Shift+.|Open profile menu

# Miscellaneous
Miscellaneous|Cmd+1|Mark as read
Miscellaneous|Cmd+2|Mark all as read
Miscellaneous|Cmd+A|Select all text in message
Miscellaneous|Delete|Delete message
Miscellaneous|Tab|Auto-complete user mention
Miscellaneous|Shift+Tab|Auto-complete reverse
